<br />
<br />I'd like to organize this again for 2012 and want to get some input on a few things:
<br />
<br />1.  Deadline
<br />2.  Voting
<br />3.  Prizes
<br />
<br />On a side note, the nintendoage people are getting <a href="http://nintendoage.com/forum/messageview.cfm?catid=22&amp;threadid=51557&amp;StartRow=51#bottom" class="postlink">antsy</a> for the multi-cart, any updates for us Memblers?

		

